    <h3>Rent Payments</h3>
    <p>Track rent collection, monitor payment history, manage your rent roll, and handle late payments efficiently.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="lb-feature-card">
    <div class="lb-icon">🔧</div>
    <h3>Maintenance</h3>
    <p>Receive, assign, and track maintenance requests from submission through resolution with full audit trails.</p>
