    <div class="lb-icon">📄</div>
    <h3>Documents</h3>
    <p>Securely store leases, insurance documents, inspection reports, and receipts — organized by property and tenant.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="lb-feature-card">
    <div class="lb-icon">📊</div>
    <h3>Financial Tracking</h3>
    <p>Monitor income, expenses, and profitability across your portfolio with real-time financial dashboards.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="lb-feature-card">
    <div class="lb-icon">🔔</div>
    <h3>Notifications</h3>
    <p>Stay informed with smart alerts for lease expirations, overdue payments, maintenance updates, and more.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="lb-feature-card">
    <div class="lb-icon">📈</div>
    <h3>Owner Dashboard</h3>
    <p>Get a complete view of your rental business — occupancy, revenue, pending tasks, and portfolio health at a glance.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="lb-feature-card">
    <div class="lb-icon">🤖</div>
    <h3>AI-Assisted Workflows</h3>
    <p>Leverage intelligent automation to streamline repetitive tasks, surface insights, and optimize your operations.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="lb-feature-card">
